ZH: 1. 他满怀信心地参加了比赛。
EN: He participated in the competition with full confidence.
ZH: 2. 她满怀希望地等待着好消息。
EN: She is eagerly waiting for good news.
ZH: 3. 这个项目的成功使我满怀自豪。
EN: The success of this project fills me with pride.
ZH: 4. 我满怀愧疚地向她道歉。
EN: I apologize to her with a heavy heart.
ZH: 5. 他满怀怀疑地看着那个陌生人。
EN: He watched the stranger with suspicion.
ZH: 6. 她满怀期待地迎接新的挑战。
EN: She is eagerly embracing new challenges.
ZH: 7. 孩子们满怀梦想地开始新学期。
EN: Children begin the new semester full of dreams.
ZH: 8. 那个年轻人满怀热情地加入了志愿者工作。
EN: The young man enthusiastically joined the volunteer work.
ZH: 9. 老师给予学生们满怀期望的目光。
EN: The teacher looks at the students with hopeful eyes.
ZH: 10. 我满怀感激地向他道谢。
EN: I thanked him with a grateful heart.
ZH: 11. 他们满怀激动地等待着演唱会的开始。
EN: They eagerly await the start of the concert.
ZH: 12. 满怀敬意，他向老师鞠躬。
EN: With respect, he bowed to the teacher.
ZH: 13. 她满怀愉快地分享自己的经历。
EN: She happily shared her experiences.
ZH: 14. 小狗满怀好奇地望着窗外的景色。
EN: The puppy looked curiously at the view outside the window.
ZH: 15. 满怀惊喜，她打开了礼物盒。
EN: Full of excitement, she opened the gift box.
ZH: 16. 满怀恶意地他对她说了一些伤人的话。
EN: He spoke hurtful words to her with malice.
ZH: 17. 他满怀怜悯地看着流浪狗。
EN: He looked at the stray dog with pity.
ZH: 18. 她满怀歉意地承认了自己的错误。
EN: She admitted her mistake with remorse.
ZH: 19. 满怀忧虑，他担心孩子们的安全。
EN: Worried, he is concerned about the safety of the children.
ZH: 20. 他满怀感激地接受了邀请。
EN: He accepted the invitation with gratitude.
